# ROS 2 Conventions

## Топики
/drone/control/rack_follower/cmd_vel      # TwistStamped
/drone/control/rack_follower/status       # String: OK/DEGRADED/FAILED
/drone/perception/barcode/detections      # BarcodeDetection.msg
/drone/perception/barcode/scan_quality    # Float32 (0.0–1.0)
/drone/perception/lidar/filtered          # PointCloud2
/drone/slam/pose                          # PoseWithCovarianceStamped
/drone/mission/state                      # String
/drone/telemetry/kpi                      # MissionKPI.msg
/drone/safety/battery_budget             # Float32

## QoS
- Сенсоры: BEST_EFFORT, VOLATILE, depth=5
- Команды: RELIABLE, VOLATILE, depth=10
- Карта/конфиг: RELIABLE, TRANSIENT_LOCAL, depth=1

## Именование
- Пакет: snake_case (rack_follower)
- Класс ноды: PascalCase (RackFollower)
- Launch файлы: Python (.launch.py), параметры из YAML
- Все velocity commanders через twist_mux
